{
  "stem": "210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, we found all these things out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And anyway, I worked in this shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in August of, of '42, all of a sudden in the morning-- and there were rumors around that they're going-- you know, that's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, they're knock on all the doors and took all the Jews out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took them to, to the temple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the temple, in the yard of the temple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the Jews were just standing, standing there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after maybe five, six hours, we were all standing there, and they came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do you say it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like a-- that all the people that worked in the shop should go on the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I didn't want to go away from my family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, all the-- my uncle, the one that, that was still-- the one that-- the tailor, he was there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and all the other people that worked in that-- in that shop, which was a lot of people, maybe 500, 600 people worked in that shop.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they all were taken to the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go away from my grand-- from my parents and my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they dragged me because I worked in the shop that I had to go too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to take me to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the time when I was in the ghetto, I was just under, you know, what they told us, that they're taking us to this ghetto and that-- you know, to this place, and that, and-- and all the other people are going to other places where they're also going to work, and you know, and survive the war.",
      "word_count": 60
    }
  ],
